title: Commonwealth, State and Territory Countering Violent Extremism Meeting 15 October 2015 (Department of the Prime ...
text: ( Source : Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet - Australian Government ) I have today convened an urgent meeting of officials from Federal, State and Territory agencies to discuss Australia's approach to countering violent extremism.
